  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - V. Ad Federicum regem.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Clausa quod effossis erumpunt ossa sepulcris,</l>
     <l n="2">Et referant veteres putria saxa rogos:</l>
     <l n="3">Nimirum tanto cupiunt sub Principe Manes</l>
     <l n="4">Vivere, et ad nutus Umbra vocata venit.</l>
     <l n="5">Utque decet, longo mansuras tempore sedes</l>
     <l n="6">Spondent, et regnis otia laeta tuis.</l>
     <l n="7">Quaeque diu ambiguis tecum fortuna vagata est</l>
     <l n="8">Passibus; hic certa stat bene nixa rota.</l>
     <l n="9">Sume animos, Federice: tuis hic meta periclis</l>
     <l n="10">Haeret: habent Manes, et pia busta fidem.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
